Interpretation boundary
-----------------------
The verification search rejected only 2 of 5,259 baseline verifications and 0 of 9,087 candidate verifications. R6 increased the aggregate verification rate, but the node delta changed sign between depths and varied strongly by position. These counters establish code-path coverage only. Suite, multiposition speed testing, and the three LOS gates remain authoritative for acceptance.
